{"tid":2394514,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"沙基利大鬧利物浦更衣室 傳不滿領隊高普戰術","createTime":"2021-02-04T08:34:29.000Z","updateTime":"2021-02-04T14:58:39.000Z","uid":44584,"like":5,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"147e0017cb759c3d879ef999cca986270ba90b83","tid":2394514,"uid":44584,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-04T08:34:29.000Z","msg":"利物浦0：1敗予白禮頓餘波未了，消息指陣中瑞士翼鋒梳頓沙基利（Xherdan Shaqiri），半場休息期間在更衣室破口大罵，對象先是隊友，繼而連領隊高普也未能倖免。<br />\n該仗比賽一面倒傾向利物浦一方，白禮頓下半場領先1：0至完場。<br />\n<br />\n英國《鏡報》消息指，沙基利主半場進入更衣室時十分憤怒，高叫：「我們理應是利物浦」（We are supposed to be Liverpool），由於他的聲浪太大，利物浦當值職員想聽不到也難，其中一人表示：「我被迫聽到他的說話。他明顯在盛怒狀態，衝入球員通道時面如玄壇。」<br />\n<br />\n「我們理應是利物浦！」<br />\n<br />\n他接着描述「瑞士美斯」如何向隊友發炮，「他指摘他們未能守護利物浦引以為傲的名字，不斷呼叫：『我們理應是利物浦（We are supposed to be Liverpool），這不應該發生。』<br />\n<br />\n該消息人士聲稱，當時也有其他人在更衣室提高聲浪，但以「瑞士美斯」聲量最大並採取主導角色。"},{"pid":"476039968c59eabd1e8510934ce485168cfcb4d1","tid":2394514,"uid":341040,"like":12,"dislike":0,"score":12,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-04T08:36:08.000Z","msg":"以為係往死裡打"},{"pid":"a2787666aed1427b0a81be8ef3b09d4835c94d8b","tid":2394514,"uid":34858,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2021-02-04T08:37:49.000Z","msg":"估唔到佢咁有火<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"59a2792b9e3b19f8be0da00e187e472c3acdbd24","tid":2394514,"uid":73381,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"a2787666aed1427b0a81be8ef3b09d4835c94d8b","tid":2394514,"uid":34858,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2021-02-04T08:37:49.000Z","msg":"估唔到佢咁有火<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-04T08:45:03.000Z","msg":"條撚樣半場比軒達臣屌鳩佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.mirror.co.uk/sport/football/news/liverpool-jordan-henderson-xherdan-shaqiri-23439139\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fww